name: GoToMeetingforAlexa
0:
”Alexa, ask go to meeting to get my meetings for today”
”Alexa, ask go to meeting to schedule a Review meeting for 9am tomorrow”
”Alexa, ask go to meeting to reschedule my Review meeting from 9am tomorrow to 11am Tuesday”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: go to meeting
des:
Get started by enabling the GoToMeeting skill in your Alexa account, linking your GoToMeeting account and adding the skill to manage your meetings. 
 
Adding this skill allows your meeting experience to become a more integrated part of your workflow each day. Manage your meetings throughout the day, wherever and whenever you need to host your session.
